BRONDAL &#8211; Police have dispersed protesting residents from the Brondal area near the Sabie/Nelspruit Road this morning.Earlier, the angry protesters blockaded the road with rocks, large wood sticks and road sign posts. &nbsp;They are demanding better accommodation from their employers.Representatives from the companies, the Thaba Chweu municipality and the other community leaders will meet this afternoon to discuss the way forward.The outcome of this meeting will determine if more protests will occur.A notice that was posted for all workers to attend the planned protestThey had gathered at the area before the protest.They also barricaded the road earlier.Protesters are gathering on the side of the Sabie road